      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You're a quick healer, I'll give you that. But, I wouldn't stop taking the antibiotics just yet, even if you're feeling better. Stopping the course too early can lead to the infection coming back, and trust me, you don't want that. I'd recommend sticking with the full 10 days and then we can reassess. In the meantime, I want you to keep taking them as prescribed, even if you're feeling fine.",
