      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my friend told me that if the bacteria are gone, the medicine is just extra stress on my liver and kidneys for no reason. if there's no inflammation left, isn't the infection technically gone? it feels like a lot of unnecessary chemicals to just keep dumping into my body when the problem is clearly solved.",
